Package com.kneelawk.commonevents.api

Annotation Interface Listen

@Retention(RUNTIME) @Target(METHOD) public @interface Listen
Used to annotate methods that listen for events.

Annotated methods should be public static and have exactly the same argument types and return type as the Event's callback interface's single abstract method.
